Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshikake! Bakunyuu Gal Harem Seikatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshikake! Bakunyuu Gal Harem Seikatsu.
